Products and services
Our banking services cover everything from credit cards to corporate banking, across the globe.



			     
			         Switzerland
             








 Parsys 1 







                                Wealth management
							



Barclays Wealth and Investment Management offers wealth management, international and private banking, trust and fiduciary services and brokerage









At Barclays we know that wealth means different things to different people. By gaining a deep understanding of your individual needs, we can offer a comprehensive and highly personalised approach to managing your wealth.
As a client you are connected to the entire Barclays Group, a major global network with offices in over 50 countries, employing approximately 140,000 people. Our service is built on over 300 years of careful financial management and broad banking expertise.
Based in Geneva since 1986, Barclays Bank (Suisse) SA caters to a diverse international client base and employs about 400 professionals. We offer services in international and private banking, investment management, investment finance and wealth structuring. We look forward to welcoming you to our offices in Geneva or in Zurich.





Go to site
View contacts













                                Investment banking
							



Deploys balance sheet in support of an origination-led banking strategy and predominantly focus on products and services with a strong track record, scale and market-leading execution capabilities









Investment Banking provides comprehensive financial advisory, capital raising, financing, structuring, risk management and execution services to banks, asset managers, pension funds, insurance companies, corporations and governments worldwide.
Our aim is to deliver first-in-class content, structuring and execution tailored to the specific client needs. We take an integrated approach to client coverage across departments, asset classes and geographies. 





