Barclays Switzerland | Barclays International | Barclays

 Hub Hero 





 Parsys 1 







Barclays in Switzerland
Switzerland is widely regarded as being one of the most attractive countries to live, work and bank.









 Parsys 2 





 Parsys 3 




Our offering
Switzerland has a unique cultural heritage, political and economic stability as its core. Its reputation as a leading financial centre is founded on strong banking regulation and strict anti-money laundering rules and a sound and reliable legal system. 
Barclays is a major global financial services provider with over 300 years of history and expertise in banking. As a leading global bank based in Switzerland, we provide our clients with state-of-the-art Wealth and Investment Management and Investment Banking expertise. 






Wealth and Investment Management
Based in Switzerland since 1986, Barclays Bank (Suisse) SA combines Swiss private banking traditions with the global resources of the Barclays network. We offer private banking, wealth structuring and investment management services to individual and corporate clients across the world. Entrepreneurs, wealth intermediaries, institutions, as well as individuals and their families, continuously turn to us to manage their wealth and benefit from our financial advice.
Our teams are located in Geneva and Zurich, which means we are ideally suited to offer our clients high quality service, combining and leveraging local infrastructure and expertise with the power and capabilities of an international bank with an extensive global network and distribution channels.
Our Private Bankers are multi-lingual professionals who strive for long term relationships and look for the most appropriate strategies and solutions to meet each client’s unique needs. 




More about Wealth and Investment ManagementMore about Wealth and Investment Management (new window) 



Investment Bank
Investment bank deploys balance sheet in support of an origination-led banking strategy and predominantly focuses on products and services with a strong track record, scale and market-leading execution capabilities. Our aim is to deliver first-in-class content, structuring and execution tailored to the specific client needs. 
Based in Zurich since 2001, our Investment Bank offers comprehensive financial advisory, capital raising, financing, structuring, risk management and execution services to banks, asset managers, pension funds, insurance companies, corporations and governments worldwide.
We focus on products and services with a strong track record, scale and market-leading capability. Our first-in-class content, structuring and execution are all carefully developed to reflect our clients’ requirements, and we take a fully integrated approach with client coverage.




More about Investment BankMore about Investment Bank (new window) 




